title: Gov't Charter 1
author: Mr__Wiggles
pages:
#- New Xiphias Orinances as of July 1st, 2013.

The former method of government as directed by the Higher and Lower Councils of Xiphias has been dissolved, and is replaced with a singular directing council, an enitity comprised of The 
#- Council Chairman TrampyCrabCake, Councilman Mr__Wiggles, and Councilman Firedart118. Mr__Wiggles is also the director of all wartime affairs and any other issues involving hostilities with sovereign entities in the absence of Council
Chairman
#- TrampyCrabCake. Councilman Firedart118 is also Director of all Economic and trading affairs in the City of Xiphias.
#- 